---
title: SuperQuick Curry Shrimp Noodles with Coconut
description: Every bite of this dish brings a burst of big flavour! Chow mein noodles are enveloped in rich coconut sauce and zesty curry paste and paired with sweet peas and vibrant peppers. A sprinkle of toasted coconut finishes this creamy, aromatic meal.

